I was tracked and notified by my ISP using this torrent.

Guys, to avoid getting tracked by your ISP, just rename the file after you've downloaded it, and maybe try converting it so the file size changes because they know the file size too. Winavi can do this. I did that with Predators after Charter sent me a copyright notice, after renaming and changing the size, even though it was still on my computer, they didn't send a second notice.
